: \"No extra dependency, Docker image, environment variable, or system property is required. The janino artifact declares commons-compiler as a normal transitive dependency, and documented Janino usage is in-process compilation through APIs such as ExpressionEvaluator, ScriptEvaluator, ClassBodyEvaluator, SimpleCompiler, and Compiler.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No special environment or system-property setup is needed. Avoid tests that rely on pre-3.1.0 internal packages such as org.codehaus.janino.util.iterator; Janino 3.1.0 moved many utility classes into commons-compiler packages while keeping the important Janino APIs stable.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The observed javac failure is from stale test code importing org.codehaus.janino.util.iterator.Iterables, not from missing test setup.\",\n    \"Meaningful native-image coverage should focus on public Janino compiler/evaluator APIs; dynamically generated classes may need normal native-test assertions or existing helper patterns rather than external setup.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00f3c20ead264811016a42cd3242ec81959bf261e01923bef2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1864, "output": 745, "cacheRead": 26112, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 28721, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782762793284, "responseId": "resp_00f3c20ead264811016a42cd29b8cc81959281c5552d47f3a2"}}
